    <item>
      <title>Centeno：若风险成为现实，欧洲央行可能考虑进一步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-22/ecb-can-weigh-bigger-cut-if-risks-materialize-centeno</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员兼葡萄牙银行行长马里奥·森特诺表示，他倾向于“逐步”调整利率，但如果经济增长出现下行风险，欧洲央行“当然可以讨论并愿意采取不同的措施”。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-22/ecb-can-weigh-bigger-cut-if-risks-materialize-centeno</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 13:52:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马蒂·弗里德森称私人信贷和美联储看跌期权正在压低垃圾债利差</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/marty-fridson-sees-private-credit-fed-put-crushing-junk-spreads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[垃圾债券专家马蒂·弗里德森 (Marty Fridson) 表示，私人债务热潮、央行支持、高国债收益率和投资者基础变化导致信贷利差人为收紧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/marty-fridson-sees-private-credit-fed-put-crushing-junk-spreads</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 13:39:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维勒鲁瓦称欧洲央行“非常有信心”实现通胀目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/ecb-very-confident-it-will-meet-inflation-goal-villeroy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦·德加洛表示，欧洲央行“非常有信心”可持续实现 2% 的通胀目标，甚至应该比 9 月份预测的更早实现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/ecb-very-confident-it-will-meet-inflation-goal-villeroy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 13:36:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
